synopsis.value: Vascular Graft Solutions (VGS) is a leading developer of innovative technologies to improve surgical revascularization, vascular reconstruction procedures and arteriovenous fistula. Our integrity and research driven development has positioned us closely to healthcare professionals, enabling us to solve complex challenges in cardiac and vascular surgery. We are improving the standard-of-care in cardiovascular surgery while focusing on patients quality-of-life, surgeons and health economics.
